Class WeightedEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spongepowered.api.util.weighted.WeightedObject<EntityType>
      • org.spongepowered.api.util.weighted.WeightedEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSerializable

    public class WeightedEntity
extends WeightedObject<EntityType>
implements DataSerializable
    Represents an entity type with a numerical weight used for random selection from a collection of weighted types.
